      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. At its heart is the 3.8L M97 flat-six engine, delivering 355 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle with a factory short-shift kit. The chassis features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for adaptive damping and cross-drilled rotors clamped by four-piston monoblock calipers. This example is in showroom condition, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a flawless DME overrev report. The original paint retains its deep luster, and the undercarriage is free of any fluid seepage or oxidation, reflecting a meticulous maintenance history.",
